        "faqSection": {
          "heading": "Frequently Asked Questions",
          "faqs": [
            {
              "question": "Is the first dental consultation free?",
              "answer": "Yes, we regularly offer free consultations and checkups for first-time visitors. Please check our website or call your nearest clinic to confirm current offers."
            },
            {
              "question": "Are your clinics open on weekends?",
              "answer": "Yes, all Clove Dental clinics are open on Saturdays and Sundays. Timings may vary by location \u2014 check your nearest clinic for exact hours."
            },
            {
              "question": "Do you offer EMI for dental treatments?",
              "answer": "Yes, we offer easy EMI options for major dental treatments. We accept cash, debit/credit cards, UPI, and EMI through leading banks."
            },
            {
              "question": "Are the dentists qualified and experienced?",
              "answer": "Yes, all our dentists are highly qualified with BDS/MDS degrees and undergo regular training in the latest dental techniques. We have specialists for every procedure."
            },
            {
              "question": "Do you offer kids dental treatment?",
              "answer": "Yes, we have specialized pediatric dentists (pedodontists) and offer complete family dental care. Some clinics also have kids play areas to ease anxiety."
            },
            {
              "question": "How do I find the nearest clinic?",
              "answer": "Use the 'Find a Clinic' feature on our website \u2014 enter your city or pincode to find the nearest clinic with directions, contact numbers, and timings."
            },
            {
              "question": "Are emergency dental services available?",
              "answer": "Yes, we provide emergency dental services to address urgent dental issues promptly. Call our helpline for immediate assistance."
            },
            {
              "question": "What sterilization standards do you follow?",
              "answer": "We follow a 10x sterilization protocol \u2014 every instrument and surface that comes in contact with patients is thoroughly sterilized before each appointment."
            },
            {
              "question": "What types of aligners do you offer?",
              "answer": "We offer various aligner brands including Invisalign, Whistle, and ClearCorrect by Straumann, tailored to individual needs and budgets."
            },
            {
              "question": "Is root canal treatment painful?",
              "answer": "No \u2014 with modern rotary endodontics and advanced pain management technology, RCT at our clinics is essentially painless and usually completed in 1-2 visits."
            }
          ]
        },
